SURVEILLANCE SYSTEMS: Installing and detecting bugging equipment

Category: Electrical
Base skill: 30% (+5%/level, cap 98%)

Installing, operating, and sweeping for surveillance equipment:
hidden cameras, listening devices, and tracking bugs. The technical
half of surveillance work, distinct from Surveillance itself (the
skill of tailing or watching a target undetected).

NOTES:
  No AetherMUD command currently rolls this skill directly. It is
  available for character concept and staff-adjudicated roleplay.

SEE ALSO: skills, electrical engineer, surveillance, detect concealment
